Results: dc:description.#text:§Method: [Observational data] The traceability of AVK treatment against grassland rodents has been ensured by the Regional Federation for Defense Against Pest Organisms and the Regional Office for Food, Agriculture and Forestry since 1991, with support from the Chrono-Environment Research Unit.  They are aggregated annualy for the Doubs and Jura départements, at commune resolution, since 1991 into a shapefile, and Excel files with raw data are stored.

They are aggregated annualy for the Doubs and Jura départements, at commune resolution, since 1991 into a shapefile, and Excel files with raw data are stored.
